name: app.R
content:
library(dplyr)
library(DT)
library(shiny)
library(shinydashboard)
library(shinyWidgets)
cssdashboard2 <<- paste0(".content-wrapper, .right-side {background-color: white !important;color: black!important; height: 5000px} 
.skin-black .main-sidebar {color: black!important;background-color: white ;font-family: 'Arial';font-size:24px;line-height:1.42857143; border: 1px outset; border-color: white !important;box-shadow: 0px 0px 2px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);} 
.skin-black .main-header {color: black!important;background-color: white ;font-family: 'Arial';font-size:24px; height: 24px !important;}
.skin-black .main-header {color: black!important;background-color: white ;font-family: 'Arial';font-size:24px; height: 24px !important;}
.skin-black .main-header .navbar { background-color: white; color: white !inportant; hieght: 10px;} .skin-black .main-header .navbar > >li > a:hover { background-color: white !important; color: white !inportant;}
.skin-black .main-sidebar .sidebar .sidebar-menu .active a{background-color: white;color: #585353; 
font-weight: normal;font-size: 24px;}.skin-black .main-sidebar .sidebar .sidebar-menu a{background-color: white;color: black;} .sidebar-menu li { margin-bottom: -15px; }
.skin-black .main-header{background-color: white;color: white; height: 24px !important;position: fixed;z-index: 100000;width: 2000px;}")
cssdashboard3 = paste0(" .skin-black .main-sidebar .sidebar .sidebar-menu a:hover{color: lightgray;}.main-header .logo {margin-left: 300px;width: 300px!important; background-color: white !important; color: black !important; height: 40px !important; font-size: 24px ; margin-left: 0px };")
divs = function(w,ml,mb,mt,bg,h) { paste0("display: inline-block;vertical-align:bottom; width:",w,";margin-left:", ml,"; margin-bottom:", mb,";margin-top:", mt,
                                          ";background-color:",bg,";height:",h,";") }
wn <<- function(z) {suppressWarnings(z)}; 
blackboxdata <<- readRDS("data.rds")
a = blackboxdata$ocean %>% select(Company,Symbol)
a = distinct(a, Symbol,Company)
place <<- blackboxdata$place %>% left_join(a, by = "Symbol")
place$ChangeN <<- ((place$Price - place$Close)/place$Close) * 100
place <<- place
ui = dashboardPage(skin = "black",title = "Black Box i",
                   dashboardHeader(title = "Black Box i"),
                   dashboardSidebar(width = 350,
                                    sidebarMenu(
                                      menuItem("History",tabName = "history"),
                                      menuItem("Outcomes", tabName = "outcomes"),
                                      menuItem("Company Bio",tabName = "company"),selcted = "history")),
                   
                   dashboardBody(
                     tags$style(HTML(cssdashboard2)),
                     tags$style(HTML(cssdashboard3)),
                     br(),
                     br(),
                     tags$div(virtualSelectInput(inputId = "stocklist",width = "350px",
                                                 label = "",choices = sort(unique(blackboxdata$ocean$Company)),search = TRUE,multiple =  FALSE)),
                     
                     
                     tabItems(
                       tabItem(tabName = "history",
                     
                     
                     div(DTOutput("datatable",width = "70vw" ), style = "font-size:85%") ))



)
)

server = function(input, output,session) {
output$datatable <- DT::renderDT({
  a = place %>% filter(Company == input$stocklist)
  a$num = NULL
  a = as_tibble(a)
  a = a %>% relocate(Date,.after = Symbol)
  a = a %>% select(Company, Symbol, Date, Price, Change = ChangeN)
  a$Change = round(a$Change,2)
  a = a %>% arrange(desc(Date))
  a = distinct(a,Date,Symbol,.keep_all = TRUE)
  datatable(a,selection = list(mode = "single", target = "cell"),rownames = FALSE,escape = FALSE,
            options = list(ordering=TRUE,searching = TRUE,lengthChange = FALSE,selection = "single",lengthChange = FALSE,paging = TRUE,
                           initComplete = JS("function(settings, json) {","$(this.api().table().header()).css({'background-color': 'white', 'color': 'black',
           'height': '50%'});","}"),
                           headerCallback = DT::JS("function(thead) {","  $(thead).css('font-size', '95%');","}"))) },,server = FALSE)
}
shinyApp(ui = ui, server = server)
